## Mutation.refundTransaction Request Mapping Template
## Invokes Lambda to process refund via payment provider
## Requires Admins Cognito group membership

{
  "version": "2017-02-28",
  "operation": "Invoke",
  "payload": {
    "action": "refundTransaction",
    "transactionId": "$ctx.args.transactionId",
    "reason": "$ctx.args.reason",
    "adminUser": "$ctx.identity.username",
    "identity": $util.toJson($ctx.identity)
  }
}
